ion and the afterlife.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aPhilosophy. 4aReligious Studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Archive Pre-2000z978311053617108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311060674440uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150170288440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501702884423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501702884/original  a978-3-11-053617-1  Cornell University Press Archive Pre-2000b2000  a978-3-11-060674-4  Cornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles